text: void main ( ) { int a , b , n , t = 0 , gcd , lcm , x , y ; scanf ( "%d" , & n ) ; while ( t < n ) { scanf ( "%d%d" , & a , & b ) ; x = a ; y = b ; while ( x != y ) { if ( x > y ) x = x - y ; else y = y - x ; } gcd = x ; lcm = ( a * b ) / gcd ; printf ( "%d %d" , gcd , lcm ) ; t ++ ; } }
